lyrics:
[verse]
In the desert sun, a restless wind blows
Through the city streets, a story unfolds
From small-time lawyer to a man on the run
A tale of redemption, just begun

[chorus]
Better Call Saul, he’ll find a way
Through legal battles, come what may
With charisma and wit, he’ll surely strive
In Albuquerque, where legends thrive
style: from the opening music from "Better Call Saul" series
